  "body": "[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I don't want Status to add contacts automatically to my contacts list so I should always have a choice to do so or not.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe the feature you would like, or briefly summarise the bug and what you did, what you expected to happen, and what actually happens. Sections below)\r\n*Summary*: Status includes contacts without my explicit confirmation. \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what you expected to happen.)\r\nI expect that Status will wait for my explicit confirmation when a contact adds me as a friend. \r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what actually happened.)\r\nIt's added automatically to my contacts list in the case described below. \r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n1. Open Status on 2 separate devices (A and B)\r\n2. Login with 2 different accounts. They should not be friends. \r\n3. Add B to A \r\n4. Send a message from A to B\r\n5. Navigate to the \"Home\" menu of B and open the 1-1 chat with A. Please note that they are not friends, yet, the \"Add to contacts\" menu is still available for B and B can't see the custom name of A.\r\n6. Select the \"...\" menu from B.\r\n7. Open the \"View profile\" menu\r\n8. Select \"Send message\"\r\nIt could be easily confirmed that A and B are now friends without the approval of B by noticing that the \"Add to contacts\" menu has disappeared and seeing the non-default profile name at the header of the chat window with A. Despite of that, I would suggest to perform the following extra steps to confirm it 100%:\r\n9. Navigate back to the \"Home\" menu of B \r\n10. Click on the \"+\" button\r\n11. Click on \"Start new chat\"\r\n12. Notice that A is presented on the \"Contacts\" list of B.\r\n\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n[comment]: # (Please summarise the solution and provide a task list on what needs to be fixed.)\r\n*Summary*: \r\n\r\n- Status should be waiting for my explicit confirmation if I want to add A to my contacts list. \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\r\n* Status version: \r\n\r\n  0.9.19 (6031) - iOS\r\n  0.9.19 (6034) - Android\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Android or iOS.)\r\n* Operating System: Android and iOS\r\n\r\n",
